  <brief_title>Radial Artery Cannulation and Perfusion Index</brief_title>
  <official_title>Does Radial Artery Cannulation Affect the Perfusion of the Dominant Hand in Patients Undergoing Open Cardiac Surgery? Data Derived From the Peripheral Perfusion Index.</official_title>
